<Members>
<Member Name="Request" DataType="STR0500" Dimension="0" Radix="NullType" Hidden="false" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Actual buffer used to build the modbus request that is transmited to the remote node.]]>
</Description>
</Member>
<Member Name="ZZZZZZZZZZraC_UDT_Mo1" DataType="SINT" Dimension="0" Radix="Decimal" Hidden="true" ExternalAccess="Read/Write"/>
<Member Name="ReqBuilt" DataType="BIT" Dimension="0" Radix="Decimal" Hidden="false" Target="ZZZZZZZZZZraC_UDT_Mo1" BitNumber="0" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Transaction request string is built, clear this if anything is changed in a read operation to rebuild the Request string.]]>
</Description>
</Member>
<Member Name="Overlap" DataType="BIT" Dimension="0" Radix="Decimal" Hidden="false" Target="ZZZZZZZZZZraC_UDT_Mo1" BitNumber="1" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Transaction is not completing before next trigger]]>
</Description>
</Member>
<Member Name="Overload" DataType="BIT" Dimension="0" Radix="Decimal" Hidden="false" Target="ZZZZZZZZZZraC_UDT_Mo1" BitNumber="2" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Transaction is not completing because of excessive Overlaps in one or more transactions]]>
</Description>
</Member>
<Member Name="TransID" DataType="INT" Dimension="0" Radix="Decimal" Hidden="false" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Serial Number of the actual Ethernet Transaction used to match to the appropriate Reply]]>
</Description>
</Member>
<Member Name="TransLastError" DataType="INT" Dimension="0" Radix="Decimal" Hidden="false" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Last Error on transaction.  0-Success, -2 Network write error, -3 Local write error, -4 Network Read Error, -5 Local Read Error, -6 Connection failed..
-12 Invalid Trans code, -13 Out of data array range.]]>
</Description>
</Member>
<Member Name="IntervalTimer" DataType="TIMER" Dimension="0" Radix="NullType" Hidden="false" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[IntervalTimer, used to trigger transaction]]>
</Description>
</Member>
<Member Name="NoReplyCounter" DataType="COUNTER" Dimension="0" Radix="NullType" Hidden="false" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[No Reply Counter]]>
</Description>
</Member>
<Member Name="PendingTimer" DataType="TIMER" Dimension="0" Radix="NullType" Hidden="false" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Timing pending requests]]>
</Description>
</Member>
</Members>
