<Routines>
<Routine Name="Logic" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[This routine unpacks the reply data for binary read operations and writes the data to the local arrays.

Check for a valid response length in bits.
Currently limited to 256, but can be increased]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[NOP();]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[[XIO(Inputs) MOV(1024,Wrk_ArraySize) ,XIC(Inputs) MOV(1024,Wrk_ArraySize) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[LES(Modbus_CMD_Len,1)GRT(Modbus_CMD_Len,256)JMP(end1);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Set up and call the _SUB_0x_WR function and call it to unpack the data and write it into the local data arrays at the LocalOffset specified in the transaction.
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[MOV(2,Wrk_BufferByteIndex)MOV(0,Wrk_BufferBitIndex)SUB(Modbus_CMD_Len,1,Wrk_Cmd_Last)ADD(Wrk_Cmd_Last,LocalOffset,Wrk_Cmd_Last)MOV(LocalOffset,Wrk_Index);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="4" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[GEQ(Wrk_Cmd_Last,Wrk_ArraySize)JMP(end1);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Here is where the data is written locally.]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[LBL(Loop)XIC(CommandString.DATA[Wrk_BufferByteIndex].[Wrk_BufferBitIndex])[XIO(Inputs) OTL(ModbusData.Coils_0xxx[Wrk_Index]) ,XIC(Inputs) OTL(ModbusData.DiscInputs_1xxx[Wrk_Index]) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="6" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIO(CommandString.DATA[Wrk_BufferByteIndex].[Wrk_BufferBitIndex])[XIO(Inputs) OTU(ModbusData.Coils_0xxx[Wrk_Index]) ,XIC(Inputs) OTU(ModbusData.DiscInputs_1xxx[Wrk_Index]) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="7" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[ADD(Wrk_BufferBitIndex,1,Wrk_BufferBitIndex)GRT(Wrk_BufferBitIndex,7)CLR(Wrk_BufferBitIndex)ADD(Wrk_BufferByteIndex,1,Wrk_BufferByteIndex);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="8" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[LES(Wrk_Index,Wrk_Cmd_Last)ADD(Wrk_Index,1,Wrk_Index)JMP(Loop);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="9" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[LBL(end1)NOP();]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
<Routine Name="Prescan" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[CLR(Wrk_BufferByteIndex)CLR(Wrk_BufferBitIndex)CLR(Wrk_Index);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
</Routines>
