</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[[XIC(KMnO4_solution_system_1.DN) ,XIC(KMnO4_solution_system_1.ER) ]XIO(KMnO4_solution_system_2.EN)MSG(KMnO4_solution_system_2);]]>
